    <h2>About the Hospital</h2>
    <p>Super Speciality Hospital Amravati is a government healthcare facility dedicated to providing advanced medical care. It offers specialized treatments and is easily accessible from the Maltekdi railway station (0.68 km away).</p>

    <h2>Services Offered</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Neurosurgery</li>
        <li>Urology</li>
